@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rrxrad(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.sin(wp.exp(tmp + 0.34)) * ((v2 + 0.66 + v0 + 0.72) * (v2 + 0.51 / v1 + 0.25)))
    tmp = (((v2 + 0.26 - v0 + 0.04) - wp.exp(v0 + 0.81)) + 0.70)
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.abs((v1 + 0.35 - v0 + 0.26)))
    v1 = (0.84 + (v0 + (tmp + 0.02 * v2 + 0.13)))
    v1 = ((0.31 * v0) / wp.sin(v1))
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.cos((v2 + 0.60 * v1 + 0.98)))
    data[tid] = v0
